I made this plugin project template for Bukkit so that you can just skip the messy process of setting up compilation, packaging and easy testing of your plugin.
A guide on how to use it can be found here:

http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/eclipse-juno-maven-craftbukkit-a-plugin-project-template.90715/

While this is public domain, a little credit would make me happier. Yours faithfully, nickguletskii200.